&lt;h2 id=&quot;other-things&quot;&gt;Other Things&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a lot of little things in LaTeX that might take some time when you’re typesetting a report or course notes, and there’s no way to cover all of them but here are a few that might be helpful:&lt;/p&gt;

